<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hóng 迦南470</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 hóngwèi shén meměilì,tā shì zhòng duō shuǐdī de héyī,
 hóngwèi shén me měi lì tā shì bǐ cǐ xiāng ài de biāo jì,
 wān wān de cǎi dàishǔ tiān de qiān bēizǒng shì jǐn mì liánjiē zài yīqǐ,
 xiàng zhe tài yáng ràng liàng guāng zhào yào, cái huì yǒu qī sè de měilì,
 cóng nèi dào wài,cóng wài dàolǐ, yī yàng bǎo guì yī yàng liàng lì,
 yǒng zài yī qǐ,yǒng yuǎn hé yī,
 hóng cái yǒu shǔ tiān de měi lì.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>470</hymn_number>
</song>